Customer: Ji client video theek hai na.

















































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































\
Executive: Hello

Executive: Hello

Customer: Haan ji.

Executive: Hello good morning sir.

Executive: Sir Shubham bol raha tha sir IndiaMART head office se sir.

Customer: Haan ho gaya Shubham bhai abhi to.

Executive: Kya keh rahe hai sir?

Customer: Ho gaya kaam jo karna tha wo to ho gaya kal.

Executive: Achcha kaam ho gaya sir? Nahi sir to mujhe bhi na kuch cheeze discuss karni thi jaise aapne waise video meet ka request dala tha kal actually hamari chutti thi na Guru Nanak Jayanti ki isliye hum kal connect nahi kar paye aapse. Theek hai? But sir isliye bata raha tha. 

Executive: Achcha aaj aapki chutti hai sir?

Customer: Theek hai. Haan.

Executive: To kal ek cheez bataye kal main aapse kis time connect kar lu kyuki mujhe na bahut sari cheeze discuss bhi karni hai kyuki aap thoda service jo aapke aap hi manage karte hai services kaun dekhta hai sir?

Customer: Main dekhta hu.

Executive: Aap hi dekhte hai? To sir kal ek baar kal to kal to open hai na sir aapka office?

Customer: Haan haan.

Executive: To kal kis time phone kar lu main aapko ek baar?

Customer: Is time.

Executive: Isi same time pe na sir?

Executive: Hello?

Customer: Haan haan.

Executive: Isi time pe kar lu na sir 11 baje ke aas pass?

Customer: Haan.

Executive: Theek hai. Baki fir main ye complaint close kar du sir aapka video meet ka jo request aaya tha ise close kar du fir main aapko. 

Customer: Haan close kar do close kar do.

Executive: Isse main close kar de raha hu aapke paas feedback aayega please feedback jarur dijiyega. Theek hai sir?

Customer: Theek hai.

Executive: Thank you sir.
